<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
  <%- include("partials/header") %>
  <body>
    <%- include("partials/nav") %>
    <div class="root-homepage">
      <header class="homepage-header">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="homepage-header-title">
              <h3>Promise-Desert 2020 早春系列</h3>
              <h2>看得清，才能看得遠</h2>
            </div>
            <a class="btn btn-sm" href="./product">立即購買</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </header>
      <section class="intro">
        <div class="container">
          <h2>用專業的心，做專業的事</h2>
          <ul class="row intro-list">
            <li class="col-md-6 col-lg-3">
              <img
                src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hexschool/2022-web-layout-training/main/week3-4/home-section2-1.png"
                alt="price"
              />
              <h3>單一價格</h3>
              <p>無論任何度數皆不需追加費用即可擁有適合自己的薄型球面鏡片。</p>
            </li>
            <li class="col-md-6 col-lg-3">
              <img
                src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hexschool/2022-web-layout-training/main/week3-4/home-section2-2.png"
                alt="efficiency"
              />
              <h3>20 分鐘即可取件</h3>
              <p>
                為了您的寶貴時間著想，以豐富專業知識與技術將結帳到交件的時間縮減至最快
                20 分鐘即可完成。
              </p>
            </li>
            <li class="col-md-6 col-lg-3">
              <img
                src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hexschool/2022-web-layout-training/main/week3-4/home-section2-3.png"
                alt="price"
              />
              <h3>安心售後服務</h3>
              <p>
                我們提供長達 120
                天的保固售後服務，不限會員資格皆享有免費深層保養及專業維修服務。
              </p>
            </li>
            <li class="col-md-6 col-lg-3">
              <img
                src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hexschool/2022-web-layout-training/main/week3-4/home-sectioin2-4.png"
                alt="price"
              />
              <h3>關於鏡片</h3>
              <p>使用世界知名頂級品牌，抗UV、防汙鍍膜薄型非球面鏡片。</p>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="category">
        <div class="container">
          <h2>經典系列鏡框</h2>
          <ul class="row">
            <li class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
              <a href="./products.html"
                ><img
                  src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hexschool/2022-web-layout-training/main/week3-4/home-section3-1.png"
                  alt="OPTICAL"
                />
                <h3>OPTICAL</h3></a
              >
            </li>
            <li class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
              <a href="./products-2.html"
                ><img
                  src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hexschool/2022-web-layout-training/main/week3-4/home-section3-2.png"
                  alt="SUNGLASSES"
                />
                <h3>SUNGLASSES</h3></a
              >
            </li>
            <li class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
              <a href="#">
                <img
                  src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hexschool/2022-web-layout-training/main/week3-4/home-section3-3.png"
                  alt="FUNCTIONAL"
                />
                <h3>FUNCTIONAL</h3>
              </a>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="co-branding">
        <div class="container">
          <h2>聯名設計鏡框</h2>
          <ul class="row co-branding-list">
            <li class="col-sm-4 col-lg-6">
              <a href="#">
                <img
                  src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hexschool/2022-web-layout-training/main/week3-4/home-section4-1-sm.png"
                  alt="DOUBLE A+"
                />
                <h3>DOUBLE A+</h3>
              </a>
            </li>
            <li class="col-sm-4 col-lg-6">
              <a href="#">
                <img
                  src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hexschool/2022-web-layout-training/main/week3-4/home-section4-2-sm.png"
                  alt="YOUTH"
                />
                <h3>YOUTH</h3>
              </a>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="comment">
        <div class="container">
          <h2>顧客推薦</h2>
          <ul class="row comment-list">
            <li class="col-sm-4 col-md-6 col-lg-3">
              <img
                src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hexschool/2022-web-layout-training/main/week3-4/home-section5-1.png"
                alt="comment-1"
              />
              <div class="comment-info">
                <span>Jessy</span>
                <p>眼鏡品質優良，下次還會想來這邊購買！</p>
                <span class="comment-date">2021/06/20</span>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="col-sm-4 col-md-6 col-lg-3">
              <img
                src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hexschool/2022-web-layout-training/main/week3-4/home-section5-2.png"
                alt="comment-2"
              />
              <div class="comment-info">
                <span>凱倫</span>
                <p>做工細緻、鏡架很輕盈，待久也不會覺得有負擔，推薦給大家！</p>
                <span class="comment-date">2021/04/18</span>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="col-sm-4 col-md-6 col-lg-3">
              <img
                src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hexschool/2022-web-layout-training/main/week3-4/home-section5-3.png"
                alt="comment-3"
              />
              <div class="comment-info">
                <span>悠悠</span>
                <p>
                  謝謝客服人員的詳細回答，成功買到了喜歡的眼鏡，下次會再回購！
                </p>
                <span class="comment-date">2020/12/25</span>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="col-sm-4 col-md-6 col-lg-3">
              <img
                src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hexschool/2022-web-layout-training/main/week3-4/home-section5-4.png"
                alt="comment-4"
              />
              <div class="comment-info">
                <span>Kyuan</span>
                <p>服務很好，品質沒有任何問題，非常喜歡。</p>
                <span class="comment-date">2020/10/31</span>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="response">
        <div class="container">
          <h2>聯絡我們</h2>
          <p class="col-sm-4 col-md-10 col-lg-6">
            我們相當重視您的意見，若您有任何疑問，可先參考「常見問題」，若仍有任何問題，請填妥以下資料，我們會在近期與您聯繫。
          </p>
          <form class="response-form col-sm-4" action="#" method="POST">
            <ul class="col-md-10 col-lg-6">
              <li>
                <div>姓名</div>
                <input
                  type="text"
                  name="username"
                  placeholder="例：廖阿杰、王小誠"
                />
              </li>
              <li>
                <div>聯絡電話</div>
                <input
                  type="text"
                  name="phone"
                  placeholder="例：0912-345-678"
                />
              </li>
              <li>
                <div>電子郵件</div>
                <input
                  type="text"
                  name="email"
                  placeholder="例：rocket@camp.com"
                />
              </li>
              <li>
                <div>意見反應</div>
                <textarea name="content"></textarea>
              </li>
              <li>
                <label class="custom-checkbox-label">
                  <input type="checkbox" name="checkbox" />
                  <div class="checkbox"></div>
                </label>
                <span>
                  我同意隱私權政策，並同意依隱私權政策中所述的方式處理自己的資料。
                </span>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <button class="col-sm-4 col-md-6 col-lg-4 btn btn-lg">
              確認送出
            </button>
          </form>
          <% if (message) { %>
          <script>
            alert("<%= message %>");
          </script>
          <% } %>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
    <%- include("partials/footer") %>
  </body>
  <script src="./src/scripts/form.js"></script>
</html>
